    "date": "2023-11-28",
    "comment": "Rationale: Cultured hippocampal neurons were immunostained for endogenous Elmod1, pre-synaptic marker protein synaptophysin (SYP) and postsynaptic marker PSD95 (DLG4). Confocal microscopy confirmed synaptic localization for Elmod1 by partial co-localization with both marker proteins. The data does not support a more specific annotation to either pre- or post-synaptic compartments.\n\n---\n\nThe experimental data annotated here will be included in an upcoming manuscript (by the SynGO consortium) that describes the SynGO 1.2 update, when a PMID is available this annotation will be updated with the respective reference.. Experimental description: Microscopy experiments were performed in cultured hippocampal mouse neurons.\n\nantibody: ThermoFisher, PA5-113204, Rabbit, poly",
